      "docs": "Origin reference to a specific decision in an ADR file. `file_path` is the project-relative path to the ADR file; stored as an opaque string since path validity is checked at file-access time. `decision_id` is the ADR decision anchor (e.g. `D1`); stored as an opaque string since format validation occurs at ADR parse time. Chain-1 evidence origins are encoded as this type.",
