      "module_path": "tddd::semantic_verify",
      "docs": "Single frozen verdict record in a semantic verify cache artifact. Extended by D3 to carry `claim_origin` and `evidence_origin` fields that identify the source artifact and location of each side of the pair. Old cache entries that lack these fields are rejected as parse errors (no backward compat, IN-08).",
